        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">This is a placeholder value that does not reflect real-world production volumes. This dataset does not currently require a real-world production volume to work in the database framework, and no actual data were collected yet. This has no negative effect on the results of the ecoinvent database. The placeholder value of this activity was scaled according to the nominal GDP of 2005 (source: United Nations, http://data.un.org/Glossary.aspx?q=GDP+%28current+US%24%29, accessed 20130726) to reflect an appropriate share of the global production volume, which is also a placeholder value.</productionVolumeComment>
